<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <!-- <title>
        Your Carbon Footprint :
    </title> -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Calibri', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            /* Calibri is preferred, fallback to other sans-serif fonts */
        }

        table {
            width: 50%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 0 0;
            /* Center the table */
        }

        table,
        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid black;
            color: #000 !important;
        }

        th,
        td {
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        p,
        h4,
        h2 {
            color: #000 !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div style="padding: 20px 0;">
        <h4>Dear <%= name %>,</h4>
        <p>Thank you for using our<strong> NetZero Platform </strong>to measure the carbon
            footprint generated from
            your <strong>
                <%= activityName %>
            </strong>activity.</p>
        <p>We're pleased to provide you with the carbon footprint report, detailing the
            emissions associated with the mentioned activity.</p>
        <h2 style="font-size: 12px; font-weight: 900;">Total Carbon Footprint :</h2>

        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>Air Travel</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalAirTravel %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Local Transportation</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalLocalTransportation %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Hotel</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalHotel %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Food & Beverages</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalFood %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Logistics</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalAirFreight %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Event Production</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totlaProduction %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Energy</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalEnergyUpdated %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Digital Comms</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalDIgitalContent %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Waste</th>
                <td>
                    <%= data.totalWaste %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <h4 class=''>Total = <%= data.grandTotal %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e</h4>
        <!-- <h4 class=''>Total tCO2e = <%= totalTonCo2 %> tCO<sub>2</sub>e</h4> -->

        <h4>For every $ you spend you are generating <%= eveydolarCo2 %> kgCO<sub>2</sub>e</h4>

        <p>We deeply value your commitment to sustainability and appreciate your proactive approach in understanding and
            mitigating your environmental impact.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance on how to reduce the carbon emissions from
            your activity, please contact at
            <a href="info@sirat.earth" target="_blank">info@sirat.earth</a>.
        </p>
        <br />
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0; font-weight: bold;">Team SirƒÅt</p>
        <!-- <a style="text-decoration:underline;color: blue;">Sirat.Earth</a> -->

    </div>
</body>

</html>